*Give Your Deliveries More Control*


Every business handles deliveries differently, some provide free deliveries
whereas others charge non-refundable shipping fees. Some may need to ensure
that riders always return the packaging material back to store.

With this update, you can now define characteristics like mandatory charges
or returnable crates in every order, ensuring complete control over what
gets delivered and what must be returned.
[image: image placeholder]


What=E2=80=99s New

