g

Rider App - Clarity on Every TripGive riders a structured view of their
tasks with no room for confusion.

   -

   Riders now see Always Deliver and Always Return sections in their
   delivery view.
   -

   These items can=E2=80=99t be modified.
   -

   COD amount adjusts automatically.
   -

   Return Order Task is created when necessary post delivery completion.

New parameter =E2=80=9Cforce_action=E2=80=9D has been introduced in the API=
 to support
this.
